%h2 Bundler API Sponsors

%p== The #{link_to 'Bundler dependency API', 'http://github.com/rubygems/bundler-api'} provides dependency information to Bundler version 1.1 and higher. It speeds up `bundle install` by several times over, but requires server capacity beyond what RubyCentral is able to provide for rubygems.org. These sponsors have provided the resources that make hosting the Bundler API possible.

